  <!-- About section -->
  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Flyy Reflections</h2>
      <p>Flyy Reflections is a luxury digital art studio and paint experience created by a Black/Mexican artist from Texas with roots in O‘ahu. Our mission is to transform grief into glam and memories into living artwork. Every design features our signature elements: cracked mirror truth, butterfly wing for you, angel wing for those we miss, chrome teardrops, and a soft baby-blue rim of hope.</p>
      <p>We believe in celebrating life through art, aligning with 11:11, and creating experiences that feel like home. Our stencils are beginner-friendly but intricate, so even first‑time painters can create something jaw-dropping. Two sessions a week leave us time to craft custom designs for each class. Digital copies of your painting are included so your memory lives on everywhere.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
